@startuml
title Conceptual Diagram of Polytech System

left to right direction

actor "Student" as student
actor "Employee" as employee

component "Web/Mobile Client" as client
component "Telegram" as telegram

package "IDEATHESIS System" as polytech {
    component "Auth Service" as auth
    component "User Service" as users
    component "Topic Service" as topics
    component "Bot Service" as bot
    component "ETL Service" as etl
}

package "External Systems" as ext_sys {
    component "University System" as unisystem
    component "GigaChat" as gigachat
}

employee --> client : uses
student --> telegram : uses

client --> auth : authenticates with
client --> users : gets user data from
client --> topics : generates/selects topics from

telegram <--> bot : interacts with (API calls)

bot --> auth : uses for authentication
bot --> users : uses for user data
bot --> topics : uses for topic management

etl --> unisystem : fetches data from
auth --> unisystem : authenticates with
topics --> gigachat : generates topics using

note left of polytech: Все сервисы системы объединены здесь\n(без API Gateway, клиенты взаимодействуют напрямую)
note left of client: Клиентское приложение (веб/мобильное)
note left of telegram: Платформа Telegram для бота
note right of ext_sys: Внешние системы, используемые сервисами

@enduml